'''Terryl Whitlatch''' (born [[April 19]], [[1960s#1960|1960]]) is a concept artist who contributed designs to the ''[[The Star Wars Trilogy Special Edition|''Star Wars'' Trilogy Special Editions]]'' and [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']]. Many of these were published in ''[[The Wildlife of Star Wars: A Field Guide]]'', which she co-wrote with [[Bob Carrau]].

==Works==
*[[The Star Wars Trilogy Special Edition|''Star Wars Trilogy Special Edition'']] {{C|conceptual design}}
*{{Film|I}} {{C|conceptual design}}
*''[[The Wildlife of Star Wars: A Field Guide]]''
*[[The Jedi Path: A Manual for Students of the Force (real-life book)|''The Jedi Path: A Manual for Students of the Force'']] {{C|images}}
*''[[Book of Sith: Secrets from the Dark Side]]'' {{C|images}}
*[[Lucasfilm]]'s [[Alien Exodus#The Alien Chronicles trilogy and Star Wars|''Alien Chronicles'']] {{C|cover artwork}}

